### Variables
### NOTE: Token is automatically synced from token.txt
### To update: Run 'php routes/tests/update_token.php' or use VS Code task "Update Token in HTTP Test Files"
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/management/dofa
@token = 

GET {{apiUrl}}?per_page=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all dofas with search filter
GET {{apiUrl}}?search=
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all dofas with status filter
GET {{apiUrl}}?status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a specific dofa by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create a new dofa (Store)
POST {{apiUrl}}/store
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Example",
    "status": 1
}

### Update a dofa
POST {{apiUrl}}/update
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "title": "Updated",
    "status": 1
}

### Soft delete a dofa
POST {{apiUrl}}/soft-delete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1
}

### Restore a dofa
POST {{apiUrl}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1
}

### Permanently delete a dofa (Destroy)
POST {{apiUrl}}/destroy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1
}

### Import dofas
POST {{apiUrl}}/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "data": [
        {"title": "Item 1", "status": 1},
        {"title": "Item 2", "status": 1}
    ]
}

### Get analytics
GET {{apiUrl}}/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
